s here? Are they cool?","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":10.6,"finishTime":13,"dialogue":{"text":"Yes, we go out with the team sometimes.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":13.2,"finishTime":14.5,"dialogue":{"text":"Are you into these activities?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":14.7,"finishTime":16.7,"dialogue":{"text":"Absolutely! They're really fun.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":16.9,"finishTime":18.1,"dialogue":{"text":"What's the team's favorite?","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":18.6,"finishTime":20.6,"dialogue":{"text":"Many of us enjoy the monthly game night.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":20.8,"finishTime":22.1,"dialogue":{"text":"Are you into board games?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":22.3,"finishTime":23.8,"dialogue":{"text":"Yes, I love board games.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":24,"finishTime":27,"dialogue":{"text":"'Monopoly' and 'Ticket To Ride' are popular choices.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":27.2,"finishTime":28.2,"dialogue":{"text":"Are you familiar with them?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":28.4,"finishTime":30.9,"dialogue":{"text":"Yes, I've played both before. Great choices.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":31.1,"finishTime":35.1,"dialogue":{"text":"Is the team into playing games on computers as well, like 'Gartic'